Metadata: The Marine Environment in Los Angeles and Long Beach Harbors during 1978. Appendix B: Biological Data for the Ports of Los Angeles and Long Beach December 1977-December 1978
Allan Hancock Foundation and the University of Southern California Sea Grant Program
Marine Studies of San Pedro Bay, California Part 17

Biological data for the ports of Los Angeles and Long Beach California December 1977-December 1978 by Harbors Environmental Projects, Institute for Marine and Coastal Studies, University of Southern California. Contents include Stations for Zooplankton Organisms Data, Plankton Data, Benthic Organisms Data, and Settling Rack Organisms (Meroplankton) data.
